summary: Here is a pretty wood elf created just for you !
descriptionHtml:
Hi ! 

That's my third preset ! Faewyn The Bosmer Hawkeye ! 

It's a Racemenu version : [size=4]I'll make [color=#00ff00]ECE[/color] version on request. =)

[/size]It might be possible to turn my presets into followers through [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54509/?]Familiar Faces[/url] mod by Verteiron if you want to ! 

[b]I add some mods to get rid of certain pixelated lips : 

- [/b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup for SKSE[/url] by Diethardt (for Mature Skin)
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2356/?]XCE[/url] by Xenius ([b][color=#ff0000]You have to install it first[/color][/b], before Better Makeup, Mature Skin and WOS - face normal maps)

[b]The required mods remain the same : [/b]

- [url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url] 
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] by expired6978
- SG Hair Pack 268 by HelloSanta
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The eyes of beauty[/url]  (Elves Edition) by LogRaam
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?] Ethereal Elven Overhaul[/url] by nuska
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32986/?]Mature skin textures V2 Beta[/url] by Maevan2
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34346/?]Smile in HD[/url] by zzjay
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34539/?]Battle hardened warpaints[/url] by Diethardt 


[b]Installation :[/b] Drop the file in your Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets\, however it's a "2[b].slot[/b]" file so [i][b]check your presets to not overwrite it[/b][/i] ! 

[b]Link to the other presets : [/b]

- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60803/?]Aenn The Fierce Nord Fighter[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60845/?]Siam the Redguard Sword Dancer[/url]

As always, endorse the mod if you enjoy and share your screenshots ! 

Quorr.
author: Quorr
